summary: Boosts your Skyrim via replacing most bottleneck code parts in the executable at runtime. Grants you major fps improvement , for ex. +50% fps gain in huge locations like Markath or Whiterun !
descriptionHtml:
[center][size=5][color=red]DO [u][b]NOT[/b][/u] USE THIS IF YOU HAVE SKYRIM VERSION 1.4 OR HIGHER. IT WILL BREAK YOUR GAME![/color][/size][/center]

Alpha version which supports 1.4 patch is published on my site, I will not publish alphas here due to possible bugs, only stable releases go here !

[b]Alyways latest version[/b]
[url=http://alexander.sannybuilder.com/?category=other&altname=skyrim_boost]http://alexander.sannybuilder.com/?category=other&altname=skyrim_boost[/url]

[b]Description[/b]
Boosts your Skyrim via replacing most bottleneck code parts in the executable at runtime. Grants you major fps improvement , for ex. +50% fps gain in huge locations like Markath or Whiterun !

[b]Supported patches[/b]
- 1.3.10.0

[b]Help the project[/b]
If you like SkyBoost project and want to help then you are welcome to visit my site , all needed details are there .
author: Alexander Blade
